</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aerimusshadowborn>Aerimus Shadowborn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 242<br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/26/03 11:10 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> well</span><hr size=1> I'd actually rather just have mannaburn be made non pvp usable personally. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=assassinite>Assassinite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/10/03 11:26 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: well</span><hr size=1> Idea for PvP balance you ask?  Convince everyone to play bards. /shrug<br>
<br>
Doesn't matter what class you are, get regal band of bathezid and a mage/druid/ranger to throw a DS on you and you're all set for a rogue killing catastrophe.  Don't even need to cast, just melee em and trigger ripostes and interrupt gate pots. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showPrevMessage?topicID=97.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showNextMessage?topicID=97.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.emailToFriend?topicID=97.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.threadControl?topicID=97.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=97.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=97.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=pos